cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning robot skills from video data. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to learn a task-agnostic skill embedding space using adversarial networks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the method learns from multi-view videos and utilizes temporal coherence to learn a disentangled representation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for unsupervised skill learning that can be applied to various tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper focuses on learning skills for robot control and demonstrates the effectiveness of the method in real-world experiments.
